  <brief_title>Fixed Dose Rate Gemcitabine and Cisplatin Followed by Chemoradiation for Locally Advanced Pancreatic Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase Ⅱ Trial of Fixed Dose Rate Gemcitabine and Cisplatin Chemotherapy Followed by Chemoradiation With Capecitabine in Patients With Locally Advanced Pancreatic Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
